data.description: Move-in ready in wonderful neighborhood. Charming character abounds in this fantastic corner lot home with hardwood floors, stone wood-burning FP and large entertaining deck. Barreled front entry matching garage, plaster walls and cove ceilings. Beautiful upgrades in kitchen and potential for over 2000sqft with basement finish. Don't miss potential roof deck off upper master bedroom. Great new biking/walking path proposed to go in on street along with new curbs that would add additional lawn along front. Don't wait on this well taken care of home with many more updates!
